OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after being
OL,4,Crescued from lake
OL,6,FA man has been rescued from a lake in
OL,7,FNewark by the emergency services, with
OL,8,Fanother man getting out by himself.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FBalderton Lake, off Heron Way in New
OL,12,FBalderton, at 14:35 on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe service said the extent of the
OL,15,Fman's injuries were not known, but
OL,16,Fupdates would be provided in due
OL,17,Fcourse.
OL,19,FThe lake is currently closed, and the
OL,20,Fpublic are being asked to stay away
OL,21,Funtil further notice.
